Reasoning: The paper deals with zero-shot learning in the context of object recognition, retrieval, and image captioning, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new formulation for learning a robust ZSL model, which involves optimization and machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the vulnerability of ZSL models to adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper presents experimental results on image datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
